Maintenance state could be part of Operational, since many devices can do background maintenance, initiated by user or automatically or remotely. (Re)configuration is also a sub-state since the device can be continuously operating also under (re)configuration. Soft reset (config reset) can also be a sub-state of Operational. From lifecycle POV, all can be seen as Operational state.
